text: Pakistan should hold a snap election and let the people decide the future.  The citizens must decide whether unnecessary spending on armaments, CPEC, useless army and terror financing is worth the pain.  Does it want to become a peaceful, progressive, intellectually capable nation  that improves the lives of all its citizens or to remain feudal, backward and the record holder of producing the highest number of donkeys.
author: Tulu Das
